  "body": "## Summary\n- Add an internal `delegate_issue` planner decision for issue-level meta orchestration while keeping `AgentAction` limited to concrete routes.\n- Create or reuse child issues with sub-orchestrator markers, dispatch child issue orchestration, and report terminal child results back to the parent issue before resuming the parent planner.\n- Move delegated route authorization to an up-front orchestrate capability check and add visible stop comments for initial guardrail stops.\n- Update orchestrator prompt/docs and add regression tests for delegation, terminal report-back, marker helpers, and authorization behavior.\n\n## Verification\n- `npm test` from `.agent`\n\nCloses #76\n",
